T02TD1937E:65a-1: bee ro tsa na ya m'a ri no pi ka n'a ma /
T02TD1937E:65a-3: gshin rje gshed rnam par snang mdzad kyi mngon par rtogs par zhes bya ba /
T02TD1937E:65a-4: rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1937E:65a-5: sangs rgyas rdo rje rtag pa'i dpal //
T02TD1937E:65a-6: me long ye shes byang chub sems //
T02TD1937E:65a-7: 'od gsal rdo rje kun zhi ba //
T02TD1937E:65a-8: ti mug rdo rje la phyag 'tshal //
T02TD1937E:65a-9: sa rnams pha rol bgrod pa'i lam //
T02TD1937E:65a-10: rtag pa'i sgrub thabs bshad par bya //
T02TD1937E:65a-11: dang por sngags pas snying rje dran pas rang lus rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD1937E:65a-12: snying gar sa bon gsal ba las ni dam pa rnams bsams nas //
T02TD1937E:65a-13: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum gyi yon tan bsam byas nas //
T02TD1937E:65b-0: bsod nams rgya cher rab tu rgyas pa'i tshogs rab @65b bsag par bya //
T02TD1937E:65b-1: byams dang snying rje dga' dang btang snyoms ldan pas stong pa bsgom //
T02TD1937E:65b-2: srung ba'i 'khor lo byas nas padma zla ba rgyas pa'i steng //
T02TD1937E:65b-3: kshe yig gyur bas chos kyi 'khor lo dmar zhing 'od 'phro ba //
T02TD1937E:65b-4: bsdu ba'i de nyid las ni rtag pa'i skur gyur pa de khro la sgeg / rtsa ba'i zhal dang gzhan gnyis dkar sngo dmar zhing phyag drug yum dang bcas //
T02TD1937E:65b-5: gri gug 'khor lo ral gri padma rin chen chu skyes rab tu 'khrugs //
T02TD1937E:65b-6: glang chen stag gi pags pas stod dang smad dkris mi mgo rlon 'dzag pa //
T02TD1937E:65b-7: thod pa drug ldan skra ni dmar ser gyen brdzes sprul brgyad yan lag spras //
T02TD1937E:65b-8: me dkyil na bzhugs ye shes sems dpa' gsal nas yan lag drug byas te //
T02TD1937E:65b-9: rlung dang me dang thod pa snod mchog sgron ma bcu yis kha bkab nas //
T02TD1937E:65b-10: bskyod dang 'bar bas glang po la sogs bcur gyur sbyor ba'i sems bab nas //
T02TD1937E:65b-12: byin rlabs rdo rje'i sbu gus rab drangs mnyes byas spro bsdus thim //
T02TD1937E:65b-13: rdo rje rtag pa rim gyis bskyod la rab thim nas ni lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba bsam //
T02TD1937E:65b-14: yod dang med pa las 'das spros bral nam mkha' lta bu'i byang chub sems dran nas //
T02TD1937E:65b-15: rmi lam sad pa'i rnal 'byor phung po khams rnams kun spangs de bzhi nas ni ldang ba brtsam //
T02TD1937E:65b-16: khams sogs bde ba chen por mdog gyur gzugs brnyan lta bur rab rtogs 'di ni rgyal sras bdag / snyig po nyi zer lta bur rdo rje'i bzlas pa 'gro ba kun la phan par bya phyir dbus du bzlas //
T02TD1937E:65b-17: rnal 'byor sgyu ma'i gzugs kyis steng 'og la spyod 'jig rten don 'gyur thams cad gshin rje gshed thob shog / aom dzin dzik mo ha ra ti /
T02TD1937E:65b-18: h'um h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1937E:65b-19: gshin rje gshed po rab 'jigs pa /
T02TD1937E:65b-20: gtu mug rdo rje'i ngo bo khyod //
T02TD1937E:65b-21: ston pa sangs rgyas kun rang bzhin //
T02TD1937E:65b-23: sgrub thabs sangs rgyas la 'jug pa //
T02TD1937E:65b-24: bskyed pa dang ni rdzogs pa'i rim //
T02TD1937E:65b-25: gong ma'i go 'phang ston pa po //
T02TD1937E:65b-26: sngags rnams sgrib pa rol gyur cig / gshin rje gshed rnam par snang mdzad kyi mngon rtogs zhes bya ba /
T02TD1937E:65b-27: rgya gar gyi mkhan po mkhas par grags pa /
T02TD1937E:65b-28: dpa' mar me mdzad kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
